# VHS tape for the README demo GIF: vhs tools/demo.tape (from repo root)
Output docs/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 680
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Hide
Type "alias uxloom='node packages/mcp-server/dist/cli.js' && clear"
Enter
Show

Type "uxloom check examples/shopmweb/uxloom.generated.project.json"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 6s

Type "uxloom check examples/shopmweb/uxloom.project.json"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
